{"tid":1552983,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Nikon FM2維修加抹鏡頭一問","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:43:51.000Z","uid":179467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"071f21efd13a883eb15615401c3ba227ecf59938","tid":1552983,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"老豆欠落一街數走咗佬唔知幾耐,早十五六年前我仲係中學雞嗰陣,我搵到佢竟然有部FM2,<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣問老母就話應該係識佢之前買嘅,不過我老豆又係唔影開相,都唔知佢買FM2嚟做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我老豆無好好照顧部相機,搞到viewfinder個菱鏡同兩支鏡都有少少發霉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我諗住讀完書出嚟先拎去俾人整,然後再自己用,不過科技發達到而家用smartphone影相都無問題,<br />\n所以我而家想整好後賣出去,俾個仲玩菲林機嘅人好過<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問香港有邊度可以抹鏡頭同菱鏡除霉?<br />\n同埋個蜂巢快門都要整一整,拉完個拉片桿後個快門自己跟住曝光,即係快門掣無咗作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008bb5c8a552340b940ca111155b361f24c8ce71","tid":1552983,"uid":13010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"你如果諗住搵人執返靚部機再賣出去，勸你慳返<br />\n<br />\n部機又唔係值錢野"},{"pid":"8490c046a08f615e4499ee150dddfd49e1c12f4f","tid":1552983,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008bb5c8a552340b940ca111155b361f24c8ce71","tid":1552983,"uid":13010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"你如果諗住搵人執返靚部機再賣出去，勸你慳返<br />\n<br />\n部機又唔係值錢野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"我唔想keep啲無用嘅嘢啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知幾耐無用過菲林 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e0a54c28a698f37280ba0607bfad7ed5ac8bed","tid":1552983,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"2k 多一點有一部。"},{"pid":"4dd9d7ccfb0ff240b7b162be8990b9bf11dc31cf","tid":1552983,"uid":8339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e0a54c28a698f37280ba0607bfad7ed5